  "details": "Capgo before 12.128.2 contains an information disclosure vulnerability in Supabase PostgREST RPC endpoints is_trial_org and is_paying_org that allows unauthenticated attackers to enumerate organizations and disclose billing status using the public sb_publishable key. Attackers can invoke these endpoints to determine organization existence via distinguishable return values and identify paying customers for targeted profiling.",
